headline.print_headline: NASCAR's Hornish at Peace Despite Uncertainty
headline.main: NASCAR's Hornish at Peace Despite Uncertainty

lead_paragraph: Most of the drivers Sam Hornish Jr. whipped on his way to winning at Iowa Speedway last week simply went on to the next racetrack.
